  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Ansible执行流程的时序图。核心参与者有四个：User、Ansible Control、Inventory和Managed Node。流程从用户执行ansible-playbook开始，最后把结果返回给用户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Ansible Control",
        "Inventory",
        "Managed Node"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那Control节点和Inventory的交互是单向的还是双向的？比如解析完inventory之后需要返回主机列表吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ansible Control",
        "Inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，是双向的。Ansible Control先向Inventory请求解析，然后Inventory返回host list给Control。之后Control才会去连Managed Node。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ansible Control",
        "Inventory",
        "Managed Node"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Control到Inventory的往返画好了。接下来是SSH连接Managed Node的部分，这里需要包含认证步骤吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ansible Control",
        "Managed Node"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要。Establish SSH connection之后，Managed Node要返回Authentication success，然后Control才会开始Gather facts。另外facts收集完还要返回给Control。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ansible Control",
        "Managed Node",
        "SSH connection",
        "Authentication",
        "Gather facts"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加SSH连接、认证和facts收集的往返。最后一步是Execute tasks吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ansible Control",
        "Managed Node",
        "Execute tasks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Execute tasks之后Managed Node返回task results，最后Ansible Control把结果Display给用户。整个流程闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ansible Control",
        "Managed Node",
        "User",
        "Execute tasks",
        "task results",
        "Display results"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "检查一遍：User触发playbook → Control解析inventory获取主机 → SSH连接并认证 → 收集facts → 执行任务 → 返回结果给用户。流程完整，我提交最终版本了。",
